SUMMARY:Rewriting the Rulebook
DESCRIPTION:From medicine to the screen; from silence to radical self-expression. \nTrinetra Haldar Gummaraju did not stumble into success — she wrote it for herself. \nBangalore Raani is a series celebrating everything women can be through candid\, unapologetic dialogue. In this edition\, Shaili Chopra joins Trinetra to talk about identity and transition: the courage it takes to live visibly as your truest self\, the loneliness and liberation that come hand in hand with being a trailblazer\, and what it really means to claim your place in spaces that weren’t built with you in mind. \nIn collaboration with: \n \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/rewriting-the-rulebook/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Bangalore,Gender,Society
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Thumbnail-47.jpg
END:VEVENT
